# Force HTTPS and canonical domain
http://sharppicks.ai/* https://sharppicks.ai/:splat 301
http://www.sharppicks.ai/* https://sharppicks.ai/:splat 301
https://www.sharppicks.ai/* https://sharppicks.ai/:splat 301

# App redirect
/app https://app.sharppicks.ai 302

# Catch-all 404 for any unmatched path. Must stay last (Cloudflare
# Pages matches _redirects rules top-down). Without this, Pages falls
# back to serving index.html for unmatched paths, which makes Google
# index phantom URLs: GSC reported /blog/<missing-slug> as 'Alternate
# page with proper canonical tag' pointing at the homepage because
# the homepage HTML and canonical were what got served. Specific
# routes above this rule still take precedence; only truly unmatched
# paths reach here.
/* /404.html 404
